OL,3,CBuckingham Palace Picture Gallery
OL,4,Cundergoes once-in-a-generation revamp
OL,6,FWATCH: ITV News London's broadcast
OL,7,Fexclusive visit to Buckingham Palace's
OL,8,Fnewly revamped Picture Gallery
OL,10,FBuckingham Palace's Picture Gallery
OL,11,Fhas undergone a major transformation
OL,12,Fready for the summer opening, with the
OL,13,Fnumber of masterpieces on display
OL,14,Falmost doubling to 120.
OL,16,FIn a striking visual revamp, the state
OL,17,Froom's coral pink velvet wall
OL,18,Fcoverings, which dated from 1976, have
OL,19,Fbeen replaced with vibrant new emerald-
OL,20,Fgreen silk damask.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
