PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783684141
OL,3,CBuckingham Palace Picture Gallery
OL,4,Cundergoes once-in-a-generation revamp
OL,6,FPaintings by Rubens, Caravaggio and
OL,7,FZoffany are among those on show for
OL,8,Fvisitors, with the new presentation of
OL,9,Fartwork taking 875 hours to hang.
OL,11,FIn what the Royal Collection described
OL,12,Fas a "once-in-a-generation re-
OL,13,Fdisplay", the number of paintings has
OL,14,Fincreased from 63 to 120.
OL,26,@tD@FOUuD@HO]
