PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783684141
OL,3,CBuckingham Palace Picture Gallery
OL,4,Cundergoes once-in-a-generation revamp
OL,6,FAdditions include Zoffany's The
OL,7,FTribuna of the Uffizi, which was
OL,8,Fcommissioned by Queen Charlotte but
OL,9,Fnever displayed in her apartments
OL,10,Fbecause she disliked its crowded and
OL,11,Funconventional composition. It was
OL,12,Flast hung in the Picture Gallery in
OL,13,F1841.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
