PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783684141
OL,3,CBuckingham Palace Picture Gallery
OL,4,Cundergoes once-in-a-generation revamp
OL,6,FVisitors will also see A Rough Dog by
OL,7,FGeorge Stubbs, believed to show George
OL,8,FIV's large pet dog, and Thomas
OL,9,FGainsborough's portrait of Johann
OL,10,FChristian Fisch, five Rembrandt
OL,11,Fpaintings and Rubens's Self Portrait,
OL,12,Fshown facing a newly-added portrait he
OL,13,Fpainted of his friend and fellow
OL,14,Fartist Anthony Van Dyck.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
