PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783684141
OL,3,CBuckingham Palace Picture Gallery
OL,4,Cundergoes once-in-a-generation revamp
OL,6,FAnna Reynolds, surveyor of the King's
OL,7,Fpictures, said: "This re-hang is an
OL,8,Fexciting and rare opportunity to
OL,9,Fsignificantly increase the number of
OL,10,Fworld-class paintings on display for
OL,11,Fvisitors, in line with our charitable
OL,12,Faim to share as much of the Royal
OL,13,FCollection as possible.
OL,15,F"It continues the longstanding
OL,16,Ftradition of renovations and re-hangs
OL,17,Fin the Picture Gallery that have
OL,18,Fcommonly taken place following a
OL,19,Fchange of reign, and we are delighted
OL,20,Fto be able to share it with as many
OL,21,Fpeople as possible this summer."
OL,26,@oD@QOUwD@AOU}D@`O]
