PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783684141
OL,3,CBuckingham Palace Picture Gallery
OL,4,Cundergoes once-in-a-generation revamp
OL,6,FThe 47-metre-long gallery, which was
OL,7,Fadded to the palace by architect John
OL,8,FNash in the 19th century, has changed
OL,9,Fcolour numerous times throughout
OL,10,Fhistory, due to shifting tastes and
OL,11,Fthe natural ageing of fabric.
OL,13,FThe room has been golden yellow, lilac
OL,14,Fwhich was fashionable in the Victorian
OL,15,Fperiod, crimson red, and then olive
OL,16,Fgreen which it remained for most of
OL,17,Fthe 20th century.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
