OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783684141
OL,3,CBuckingham Palace Picture Gallery
OL,4,Cundergoes once-in-a-generation revamp
OL,6,FIt was switched to pink 50 years ago
OL,7,Fand now, amid the deterioration of the
OL,8,Fmaterial, has been spruced up with a
OL,9,Fchange to emerald green.
OL,11,FThe room is used by the royal family
OL,12,Fto host guests, with presidents `
OL,13,Fincluding Donald Trump in 2019 ` and
OL,14,Fmonarchs being taken on a tour to see
OL,15,Fa special exhibition of Royal
OL,16,FCollection items in the gallery when
OL,17,Fstate visits are hosted at the palace.
OL,19,FThe gallery is also seen by more than
OL,20,Fhalf a million visitors each year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
