FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783684141
OL,3,CBuckingham Palace Picture Gallery
OL,4,Cundergoes once-in-a-generation revamp
OL,6,FThe transformation was unveiled a
OL,7,Ffortnight after it was announced the
OL,8,FKing and Queen will never live at
OL,9,FBuckingham Palace.
OL,11,FCharles and Camilla will stay at
OL,12,Fnearby Clarence House instead, keeping
OL,13,Fthat as their London home, despite the
OL,14,F#369 million renovation of the palace.
OL,16,FThe summer opening of Buckingham
OL,17,FPalace runs from July 9 to September
OL,18,F27 this year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/8
